            + `reduce`
            + `hide`
            + `show`

### Single Insert or Delete Col [POST]
    
+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            excelId: 28b60797-8457-4410-8fac-db1161839cc7
    
    + Attributes (Col Number)
    
+ Response 200

## Adjust Single Col Width [POST /col/adjust]

    列宽调整
    
+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            excelId: 28b60797-8457-4410-8fac-db1161839cc7
    
