# Group Sheet Opration

## Table Paste [/sheet/paste]

### Paste All Info to Any Where [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            excelId: 28b60797-8457-4410-8fac-db1161839cc7
    
    + Attributes (Operation Coordinate)
        + colLen: 1 (number) - 粘贴数据的列数
        + rowLen: 1 (number) - 粘贴数据的行数
        + pasteData (array[Paste Object]) - 被格式化完的数据
        
+ Response 200 (application/json;charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes
        + isLegal: true(boolean) - 是否合法
    
+ Response 400

## Table Cut & Copy [/sheet/{actionType}]

+ Parameters
    + actionType: `cut`(string)
        这个动作是剪切或者复制，这个动作的触发只能在excel出现，跟外部交互的操作都是粘贴操作，
        由于浏览器的保护，数据不能获取被剪切到外部的事件
        + Members
            + `cut`
            + `copy`

### Cut or Copy Info to Any Where [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            excelId: 28b60797-8457-4410-8fac-db1161839cc7
    
    + Attributes
        + orignal (Coordinate properties) - 数据原来的位置
        + target (Operation Coordinate)
        
+ Response 200 (application/json;charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes
        + isLegal: true(boolean) - 是否合法

+ Response 400

